snippet.title: Astra Protocol 2 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Monitors have received notification of an unknown event, referred to as ASTRA PROTOCOL. You have been designated search and reconnaissance to determine the meaning of this ASTRA PROTOCOL. SECONDARY OBJECTIVE: Find evidence of survivors. PROBABILITY OF HOSTILES: HIGH.

Astra Protocol 2 is coming to Steam in December: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2026750/Astra_Protocol_2/

For more information:
Website: https://slicebar.games/games/astra-protocol-2/
Press Release: https://slicebar.games/games/astra-protocol-2/astra-protocol-2/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/slicebargames
